What you need to know:  Boomplay has a diverse music catalogue of 95 million songs from across Africa and globally. It gives artists – both men and women alike – the opportunity to earn from their musical talent, thus enabling a more inclusive music industry.Together with its partners, Boomplay has shown that it is possible for women musicians – and performing artistes in general – to fully unlock their potential. Women artistes have pushed their foot in and there’s no turning back because the African society is, thankfully, gradually embracing equity.